{"word":"ἐπιζήμιος","slug":"ἐπιζήμιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιζήμιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ζημία'><el>ζημία</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>bringing loss upon, hurtful, prejudicial</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>penal</i>: —<el>ἐπιζήμια, τά</el>, <i>penalties</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>liable to punishment</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}